Title: Underwater Menace
Description: Did you see that? Underwater! A huge, armored, hungry beast! No way I'm getting near water with my net while that monstrosity lurks below. If you want, you can likely lure out with a handful of Ominous Conches, those shouldn't be too hard to catch.
ObjectivesText:
Use 5 Ominous Conches in the Tyrhold Fishing Hole to summon a huge underwater beast, and bring back something as a proof of its demise.

You may unlock only one extra fishing net per day.
